{"word":"σφραγίζω","slug":"σφραγίζω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>σφραγίζω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:σφραγίς\">σφραγίς</a></el>] ‘certify with a mark’, <b>seal<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> to make secure: a stone at a tomb <b><a href='B:470 27:66'>Mt 27:66</a>;</b> entrance to an abyss <b><a href='B:730 20:3'>Rv 20:3</a>.</b> In related vein, to maintain secrecy <b><a href='B:730 10:4'>10:4</a>; <a href='B:730 22:10'>22:10</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> to indicate ownership <b><a href='B:500 6:27'>J 6:27</a>; <a href='B:520 15:28'>Ro 15:28</a>; <a href='B:730 7:3-5'>Rv 7:3-5</a>, <a href='B:730 7:8'>8</a>.</b> In imagery<b> <a href='B:540 1:22'>2 Cor 1:22</a>; <a href='B:560 1:13'>Eph 1:13</a>; <a href='B:560 4:30'>4:30</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp></b> to guarantee <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a>, in imagery <b><a href='B:500 3:33'>J 3:33</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:σφοδρῶς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:σφραγίς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}